## Location

- District 7, Saigon, Vietnam

- Fulltime

Sendo.vn is the online marketplace of FPT Group which connects buyers and sellers around the country. Originally an e-commerce project of FPT Online JSC, Sendo.vn was officially launched on Sept 2012. On May 13rd 2014, Sendo Technology JSC was founded as a member of FPT Group and is responsible for operating Sendo.vn marketplace.

Up to now, more than 80,000 shops have been operating on Sendo.vn, offering a diverse range of products with over 5 million products from 21 different categories.

## Salary Expectation

* up to 45mil

## Requirements
* Bachelor's Degree in any relevant major (Software Engineering, Computer Science, ect.);
* 3 years experience in PHP or 1-2 year experience in Golang;
* Strong proficiency working with database systems such as MySQL, MongoDB
* Have knowledge and experience with Elastic Search/Redis/Memcached; Git and Repository Management;
* Have experience about Linux (Ubuntu, OSX);
* An understanding and experience in working for large scale system;
* Experienced working with Scrum/Agile Process
* Ability to work both independently and as a team member;

### Responsibilities

* Building e-commerce’s core system of Sendo.vn;
* Developing scalable new features for our website;
* Building architecture for our platform to ensure optimal performance;
* Obtaining requirement feedback from internal teams/clients to maintain/support the product development;
* Performing code reviews on other team member’s work;
* Do research and apply new technologies to bring the best user experiences;
* Work collaboratively with Seller Center, Order Processing Center, System and RAD teams to establish new requirements, project priorities and other important aspects of Client Requests.

### Why it would be awesome to work with us

- Competitive compensation package: 13th month- salary and 1-3 months bonus salary
- Performance review: 2 times/ year
- FPT Care Health Insurance
- 18 days annual leave
- Applicable for all normal benefits: insurances, annual company trip, team building activities

